Bulletin board inherit 

The board inherit should be able to :
Enable players to post      
List all posts.
Store posts.
Auto remove posts after a given time.
Remove posts by the poster or owner of board.
Display one post.
Have a catchup facility.
Have sticky posts (Can't be autoremoved at board owners discression)

Enable players to reply to a specific post (Reply <#>) and the board could
 keep track of this fact and display posts sorted by topic order _or_ date
 order. (or by topic and within each topic by date) /* Tim */
Use the global editor to get text from the player. /* Tim */
